              <img src="https://assets.fireside.fm/file/fireside-images/podcasts/images/0/0bf56c68-56e1-4d3d-a595-47a8227512d5/hosts/1/16717c6b-829f-4bfd-ae27-8bd9c94e17fd/avatar_small.jpg">
